PROJECT ENGINEER - CIVIL-INFRASTRUCTURE - OFFSHORE - OIL&GAS; industry experienced candidates are required for a
Leading Oil & Gas Group Co. in Abudhabi, UAE -
Attractive Salary + 42 days p.a., Family Accommodation @ AED 2,25,000 plus furniture purchase allowance, Education Assistance, Insurance, Free Medical, End of Service Benefit, etc.
Duties :
To Plan,
manage and direct activities for Infrastructure Projects and utilities - Offshore (all phases) - OIL&GAS-DESIGN-PLAN-CONSTRUCTION-OPERATIONS-Commissioning; to handover-EPC PROJECTS, Site Operations, Technical Definitions, Design, Estimates, Budgetting, Project Implementation Strategy,etc.
Desired Candidate Profile
Bachelor Degree in Civil Engineering with total experience of not less than 15 years in the Infrasture & Utilities Field- Oil & Gas Industry - Gulf/UAE exp.
CIVIL-PROJECT ENGINEER-INFRSTRUCTURE-OIL&GAS-OFFSHORE-DESIGN-PLAN-CONSTRUCTION-OPERATIONS-FEED-BUDGET-PROJECT; IMPLEMENTATION STRATEGY-EPC-PIPELINE - PIPING SYSTEM-HSE.
Proficient in Written/Oral English, MS-Office & ERPs,etc.
